          <comment xml:lang="en">The price is from the year 2020. Price information has been directly provided by the data provider based on the following reference: University of Minnesota, Machinery cost estimates, W.F. Lazarus, 2020. The prices were adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/STS_INPP_A__custom_6416181/default/table?lang=en, last accessed on 2023-06-01).</comment>
