        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Area of sugarcane, arable crops, permanent meadows and pasture, year 2020, according to the FAOSTAT data. This operation is assumed to occur every 5 year in sugarcane and every 7 years in permanent meadows and pasture.</productionVolumeComment>
